        return "Yes, After Degree completion, Degree Convocation takes place at SIU and we provide an industry-recognized certificate upon successful completion of various internships and courses."

    elif "faculty" in user_input or "teachers" in user_input:
        return "Our faculty includes experienced professionals from industry and academia with a vast years of exeperience of core subjects ."

    elif "placement" in user_input or "job" in user_input:
        return "We provide placement assistance with top companies in IT and analytics, providing rewarding packages in top Companies."

